  "narrative_for_user": "Pre-exhaustiveness review refused: two plan items (pli_006, pli_007) still show in_progress even though both are environment-blocked. The fix is bookkeeping — set both to skipped. Separately, the bride's person_id is the literal placeholder 'PID-TODO' throughout the evidence links; that needs to be replaced with a real tree ID before a proof conclusion can name her specifically. Once those two items are resolved, re-invoke the mentor for the full substantive review.",
